name: Weiss Schnee RWBY (Embedding)
description:
Weiss Schnee from the RWBY web series.

I'm not happy with this BUT I think it's good enough to let you great people play around with it.

Besides I've put too much time into it to not share it.

This one is a bit messy as you need to specify her outfit or you get an amalgamation of all of them, which can look good model dependant.

Embedding Trained using 120 Images from various sources including the show, the anime, some fan art (including NSFW) and even cosplayers. Including the training data if someone wants to try to and make their own, please do. (It's the same pictures as the LORA but without the "Weiss Schnee" Tag)

Works best with the LORA I'll upload as well (trying to get to a point where either can stand on their own but no good so far).

Weiss Schnee [LORA] | Stable Diffusion LORA | Civitai

Let me know what you think.
